    "tacoma:hub:a12d6fbf58e4434b8ff5070c09646f19": {
      "itemDescription": "<div style='text-align:Left;'><p><span>Permit data extracted from Accela permitting system.\u00a0</span>The script runs daily and pulls all of yesterday's Accela updates. Some of them are new records, but the majority are updates to the status of existing records.\u00a0</p><p>Users can also search for records via the\u00a0<a href='https://aca-prod.accela.com/TACOMA/Default.aspx' target='_blank' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'>Customer Access Portal</a>.</p><p>Contact:<br />Nathan Connors &amp; Jason Hildreth (IT)<br /><br /></p></div>",
